{"tid":2007510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"現實同你講，誰大誰惡誰正確","createTime":"2020-05-08T11:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T11:34:34.000Z","uid":220864,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ce5d67b51b246cae5e91ddcc48b4ae1987bd5798","tid":2007510,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:04:48.000Z","msg":"今日郭偉強同陳志全條片好多人share<br />\n但係想同大家講，其實而家呢個時候再搏同情攞分已經無用<br />\n<br />\n我見到條片有第二個諗法<br />\n屌你老味人地一隻手可以玩弄你<br />\n拖住你當狗走<br />\n你弱到咁點抗爭<br />\n<br />\n其實而家唔再係需要做show<br />\n因為對錯已經變成由強者去決定<br />\n你比人拖住嚟行<br />\n對家都係會話你地暴力<br />\n道理根本唔係用講<br />\n<br />\n想同立法會入面班人講<br />\n你地嗌口號舉牌同衝去主席枱已經用到舊<br />\n可唔可以進步?<br />\n唔係叫你打柒佢<br />\n人地保安夾你走你放鬆個人?<br />\n咁不如你自己走出去算"},{"pid":"0989897f0f32a787a191439f49ffdb0868360085","tid":2007510,"uid":220864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:05:46.000Z","msg":"唔該議員反省下<br />\n有咩方法比多d壓力人<br />\n唔係尻嗌<br />\n<br />\n咁樣落去下屆唔應該係你地做"},{"pid":"32d0ea11ceba908b681e5f66f91c48495b0d88dc","tid":2007510,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:06:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a598c3670bbe8d7c7cf6b0d24f9a93e10e8f4c2c","tid":2007510,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:06:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42ec7d029a61de3208f889410b3a3e7e31d8c7f8","tid":2007510,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:06:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d73d3d43586dd37f571084accddfd24d57a61c3b","tid":2007510,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c8bbbda2dbd8e9a14d91c68136d6dd66898c3e1","tid":2007510,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:06:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ea8276cbd1ede266bbd92978188649fc7497de5","tid":2007510,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:07:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b5cc061d31df